column5: Any of you folks ever fished these lakes or know anything about them that you can share???

Not sure I've heard or read too many reports on OFC over the years that name those 2 lakes....however you really can't go wrong for eyes and pike in the Chapleau region.  I think there are a few lodges on Anjigaming....maybe their websites will provide a bit of info?
Anjigaming...never heard of it, Anjigami yup
